{"id": "art-39", "label": "Art. 39", "title": "Art. 39", "slug": "art-39", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 39 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1996296614\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2466\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1996296614\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>Nu pot fi <span class=SpellE>numi&#355;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>exper&#355;i</span>:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_877014677\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2465\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_877014677\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)rudele sau afinii pân&#259; la gradul al IV-lea inclusiv\nori <span class=SpellE>so&#355;ii</span> acelora care au constituit aporturi în\nnatur&#259; sau ai fondatorilor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1353360138\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2464\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1353360138\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)persoanele care primesc, sub orice form&#259;, pentru <span\nclass=SpellE>func&#355;iile</span> pe care le îndeplinesc, altele decât aceea\nde expert, un salariu ori o <span class=SpellE>remunera&#355;ie</span> de la\nfondatori sau de la cei care au constituit aporturi în natur&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1140751261\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2463\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1140751261\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)orice persoan&#259; c&#259;reia, ca urmare a <span\nclass=SpellE>rela&#355;iilor</span> sale de afaceri, de munc&#259; sau de\nfamilie, îi <span class=SpellE>lipse&#351;te</span> <span class=SpellE>independen&#355;a</span>\npentru a realiza o evaluare obiectiv&#259; a aporturilor în natur&#259;,\npotrivit normelor speciale care reglementeaz&#259; profesia.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}